{"id": 7401, "title": "Ticket #7401: GCE gahp has issue with SSL after running for a \"long time\"", "description": "<blockquote>\nAfter running for something on the order of two weeks, the GCE gahp suddenly stops being able to authenticate.  Restarting it seems to fix the issue.\n\n<p>We were never able to reproduce or debug this issue.  As a workaround we propose adding GCE_GAHP_LIFETIME, after which the gahp will exit and be restarted by the gridmanager.\n\n</p><p>This now happens by default every 24 hours.  This will not affect the jobs themselves.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2019-Dec-02 16:06:09 by jfrey:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>Code Review</strong>\n\n<p>The code for this looks fine.\n\n</p><p>I suppose we should document this new config knob.\n</p><hr/>\n<em>2020-Apr-10 07:46:37 by tim:</em> <br/>\n\nBulk change of target version from v080906 to v080907 using ticket-target-mover.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Dec-11 13:32</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/1354999f6d6ba6db95354799ff1c66206e08a903\">[58637]</a></span>: Docs and version history for gce_gahp issue. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7401\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7401'); return false;\" title='GCE gahp has issue with SSL after running for a \"long time\"'>#7401</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Dec-11 13:08</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/74f2f445a2c5a906e5afad1115031bc40ede8c4a\">[58636]</a></span>: Make default to restart gce_gahp every 24 hours. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7401\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7401'); return false;\" title='GCE gahp has issue with SSL after running for a \"long time\"'>#7401</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Nov-25 19:13</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/1c89412a7fb93afa9fb4984f152029b721ffdeac\">[58553]</a></span>: param_integer, not param_int <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7401\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7401'); return false;\" title='GCE gahp has issue with SSL after running for a \"long time\"'>#7401</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Nov-25 16:06</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/ed825b0fa750e7fd6d7fa2b90a63fb53e7e4d6d5\">[58549]</a></span>: Add a parameter for causing the GCE gahp to self-exit after some time. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=7401\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7401'); return false;\" title='GCE gahp has issue with SSL after running for a \"long time\"'>#7401</a></span>  (By zmiller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "defect", "last_change": "2020-Apr-10 07:46", "status": "resolved", "created": "2019-Nov-25 16:05", "fixed_version": "2019-Nov-25 16:05", "broken_version": "v080900", "priority":